{"word":"παραχέω","slug":"παραχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραχέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-χεῶ</el>) (aor1 <el>-έχεα</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-κέχῠκα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to pour in beside, pour in</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of solids, <i>to heap up on the side</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to lie spread out near</i>, of a country, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}